title: Ep. - 447 - LOVE IS BLIND 2 WITH MATT AND JAKE LOVE OFF THE GRID WITH CHRIS FARAH
description:
Matt and Jake from Reality Gays podcast help Kate review Love is Blind 2 on Netflix, a series which follows 30 men and women hoping to find love. For 10 days in a speed-dating format, the men and women date each other in different "pods" where they can talk to each other but not see each other. Whenever they decide, the men are able to propose to the woman they want to marry.

 

Comedian and host Chris Farah reviews Love Off the Grid on Discovery+, which follows four people accustomed to modern amenities who give it all up for a chance at true love since their partner lives off the grid.
